  subtitleEcosystem1: "Synergy with 304 & Rojana Industrial Parks",
  textEcosystem1: "The property is adjacent to two of Thailand's premier industrial estates: 304 Industrial Park and Rojana Industrial Park. This proximity provides a \"halo effect,\" granting access to a proven ecosystem with established infrastructure, support services, and a history of attracting major foreign investment. Investors benefit from this mature environment without being subject to the specific management fees of those parks.",
  subtitleEcosystem2: "Major Multinational Corporations & Supply Chain Opportunities",
  textEcosystem2: "The area is a dense cluster of global manufacturing giants, particularly in the automotive and electronics sectors. The presence of Tier-1 and Tier-2 suppliers creates immense supply chain synergies. New investors can source high-quality components locally, reducing logistics costs, while new component manufacturers gain immediate access to a large, consolidated customer base.",
